text: @FedExHelp My package is in my area, called so I could pick it up, as it is an inportant package, was denied, and told there was a hold and the package would not and could not be sent out becuase the sender “requested” the hold. Is there any way around this?

@DaveBeeStocks @DaveBeeStocks Dave, hello this is Joe. I do apologize on behalf of Fedex for this issue with your package delivery. Please DM @FedExHelp recipient name, delivery address, tracking & phone numbers. I would be happy to research this matter.
~joe
